## 安裝
```bash
composer create-project laravel/laravel my-app
cd my-app
php artisan serve
```

## Migration
```bash
php artisan make:migration create_posts_table
```

```php
public function up()
{
    Schema::create('posts', function (Blueprint $table) {
        $table->id();
        $table->string('title');
        $table->text('content');
        $table->foreignId('user_id')->constrained();
        $table->timestamps();
    });
}
```

```bash
php artisan migrate
```

## Model（Eloquent）
```php
class Post extends Model
{
    protected $fillable = ['title', 'content', 'user_id'];

    public function user()
    {
        return $this->belongsTo(User::class);
    }

    public function comments()
    {
        return $this->hasMany(Comment::class);
    }
}
```

## Eloquent 查詢
```php
// CRUD
$post = Post::create(['title' => '...', 'content' => '...']);
$post = Post::find(1);
$post->update(['title' => 'New title']);
$post->delete();

// Query
$posts = Post::where('user_id', $user->id)
    ->orderBy('created_at', 'desc')
    ->limit(10)
    ->get();

// Relations
$posts = Post::with('user', 'comments')->get();

// Aggregates
$count = Post::where('published', true)->count();
$total = Order::sum('amount');
```

## Controller
```bash
php artisan make:controller PostController --resource
```

```php
class PostController extends Controller
{
    public function index()
    {
        return Post::with('user')->paginate(20);
    }

    public function store(Request $request)
    {
        $validated = $request->validate([
            'title' => 'required|string|max:255',
            'content' => 'required'
        ]);

        $post = $request->user()->posts()->create($validated);
        return response()->json($post, 201);
    }

    public function show(Post $post)
    {
        return $post->load('user', 'comments');
    }

    public function update(Request $request, Post $post)
    {
        $this->authorize('update', $post);
        $post->update($request->validated());
        return $post;
    }

    public function destroy(Post $post)
    {
        $this->authorize('delete', $post);
        $post->delete();
        return response()->noContent();
    }
}
```

## Routes
```php
// routes/api.php
Route::middleware('auth:sanctum')->group(function () {
    Route::apiResource('posts', PostController::class);
});
```

## Validation
```php
$request->validate([
    'email' => 'required|email|unique:users',
    'password' => 'required|min:8|confirmed',
    'age' => 'required|integer|min:18'
]);
```

## Auth（Sanctum）
```bash
composer require laravel/sanctum
php artisan migrate
```

```php
// Login
public function login(Request $request)
{
    $request->validate(['email' => 'required|email', 'password' => 'required']);

    if (!Auth::attempt($request->only('email', 'password'))) {
        return response()->json(['error' => 'Invalid credentials'], 401);
    }

    $token = $request->user()->createToken('api')->plainTextToken;
    return ['token' => $token];
}
```

## Queue（背景任務）
```bash
php artisan make:job SendWelcomeEmail
```

```php
class SendWelcomeEmail implements ShouldQueue
{
    public function handle()
    {
        // 寄信
    }
}

// 派
SendWelcomeEmail::dispatch($user);
```

跑 worker：
```bash
php artisan queue:work
```

## 心法
- Laravel 是 PHP 的 Rails
- Eloquent 寫得超爽
- artisan CLI 神器
- 生態完整、社群大
- 快、容易 ship MVP

**☕ 用人話講**

Laravel 起步 + Eloquent ORM——**寫起來像 Ruby on Rails，「約定優於配置」**。**一句話記住**：像一套有固定套路的工具箱——Laravel 把常見的後端工作標準化，照著約定做，又快又整齊。

